# Quick Reference

**App root:** tutti i percorsi sotto sono relativi a `easytrip-saas/` (esegui i comandi npm da quella cartella).

## Common Commands

```bash
cd easytrip-saas

npm run dev          # Next.js dev (--webpack)
npm run build        # Production build
npm start            # Production server
npm run lint         # ESLint
npm run format:check # Prettier (stesso check della CI)
npm run typecheck    # tsc --noEmit (stesso check della CI)
npm run test:unit    # Vitest unit
npm run test:e2e     # Playwright E2E
npm run inngest:dev  # Inngest dev server (vedi package.json)
```

**CI su GitHub:** vedi [`docs/DEPLOYMENT.md`](../easytrip-saas/docs/DEPLOYMENT.md) (sezione CI) — workflow `.github/workflows/main.yml`.

## File Locations (in `easytrip-saas/`)

- **Documentation:** `docs/`
- **Static assets:** `public/`
- **Utility scripts:** `scripts/`
- **Source code:** `src/`
- **Test files:** `tests/`
- **Prisma:** `prisma/`

